<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      background: #F47C20;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .button {
      background: #F47C20;
      color: #333333;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Our Platform!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining our platform. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
      <p>You can now login to your account and start exploring all the features we offer.</p>
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Get Started</a>
      </p>
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team {{supportEmail}}.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>